          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>Gaming peripheral manufacturer SteelSeries is running a limited-time Buy One Get One 50% Off deal for Valentine's Day at its official online store. All SteelSeries accessories are eligible for the deal, including the company's new <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsteelseries.com%2Fgaming-headsets%2Farctis-gamebuds-for-playstation-us%3Fcolor%3Dblack&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fsteelseries-valentines-day-sale-buy-1-get-1-50-off-gaming-accessories%2F1100-6529340%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Arctis GameBuds</a> wireless gaming earphones, making now a great opportunity to upgrade your gaming setup for you and your partner. To get the B1G1 50% Off deal, you need to add two SteelSeries products to your cart, then use the promo code <strong>VALENTINE50</strong> at check out, and you'll receive a 50% discount on the lowest-price item.</p><h3 dir="ltr">Shop all SteelSeries products:</h3><ul><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsteelseries.com%2Fgaming-headsets%3Fin_stock%3Don&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fsteelseries-valentines-day-sale-buy-1-get-1-50-off-gaming-accessories%2F1100-6529340%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Headsets</a></li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsteelseries.com%2Fgaming-speakers&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fsteelseries-valentines-day-sale-buy-1-get-1-50-off-gaming-accessories%2F1100-6529340%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Speakers</a></li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsteelseries.com%2Fgaming-keyboards%3Fin_stock%3Don&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fsteelseries-valentines-day-sale-buy-1-get-1-50-off-gaming-accessories%2F1100-6529340%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Keyboards</a></li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsteelseries.com%2Fgaming-mice%3Fin_stock%3Don&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fsteelseries-valentines-day-sale-buy-1-get-1-50-off-gaming-accessories%2F1100-6529340%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Mice</a></li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsteelseries.com%2Falias&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fsteelseries-valentines-day-sale-buy-1-get-1-50-off-gaming-accessories%2F1100-6529340%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Microphones</a></li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsteelseries.com%2Fgaming-mousepads%3Fin_stock%3Don&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fsteelseries-valentines-day-sale-buy-1-get-1-50-off-gaming-accessories%2F1100-6529340%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Mousepads</a></li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsteelseries.com%2Fgaming-controllers%3Fin_stock%3Don&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fsteelseries-valentines-day-sale-buy-1-get-1-50-off-gaming-accessories%2F1100-6529340%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Controllers</a></li></ul><p dir="ltr">If you're looking for some recommendations, we would start with the <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsteelseries.com%2Fgaming-headsets%2Farctis-gamebuds-for-playstation-us%3Fcolor%3Dblack&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fsteelseries-valentines-day-sale-buy-1-get-1-50-off-gaming-accessories%2F1100-6529340%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Arctis GameBuds</a> mentioned above. The $160 GameBuds are the newest addition to SteelSeries' Arctis line of gaming headsets and audio devices. They're the company's first set of true wireless gaming earbuds, and this B1G1 50% Off deal is the first time they've been available at a discount. Granted, you have to pick them up with another SteelSeries accessory to unlock the deal, so you'll be paying more than you normally would for just the GameBuds by themselves, but you'll still save quite a bit on your order--especially if you pair it with a product that's already discounted. For example, you can grab the GameBuds and the <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsteelseries.com%2Fgaming-mice%2Faerox-3-2022%3Fconnectivity%3Dwired%26mouse-body-color%3Donyx&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fsteelseries-valentines-day-sale-buy-1-get-1-50-off-gaming-accessories%2F1100-6529340%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Aerox 3 2022 Edition gaming mouse</a> that's on sale for $40 (was $60). With the B1G1 50% off discount, you'll pay just $180 total for both items.</p><p dir="ltr">Some other worthwhile accessories to pick up in the sale include other Arctis audio devices like the stellar <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsteelseries.com%2Fgaming-headsets%2Farctis-nova-pro-wireless-pc-playstation%3Fcolor%3Dblack&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fsteelseries-valentines-day-sale-buy-1-get-1-50-off-gaming-accessories%2F1100-6529340%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Nova Pro</a> and <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsteelseries.com%2Fgaming-headsets%2Farctis-nova-7&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fsteelseries-valentines-day-sale-buy-1-get-1-50-off-gaming-accessories%2F1100-6529340%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Nova 7</a> wireless headsets. If you prefer a speaker setup, there's the <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsteelseries.com%2Fgaming-speakers%2Farena-7&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fsteelseries-valentines-day-sale-buy-1-get-1-50-off-gaming-accessories%2F1100-6529340%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">SteelSeries Arena 7 Speakers</a>. And if you need a new keyboard, there's the <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsteelseries.com%2Fgaming-keyboards%2Fapex-pro-mini-wireless&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fsteelseries-valentines-day-sale-buy-1-get-1-50-off-gaming-accessories%2F1100-6529340%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Apex Pro Mini Wireless</a> that's just $190 (was $240).</p><p dir="ltr">Head over to SteelSeries to see the company's full lineup of gaming accessories. Most of SteelSeries' products are for PC, but many also work on consoles, including its many headsets, earphones, and speakers. However, if you're looking for some console-specific gear deals, Sony is offering a similar discount for <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/ps5-accessory-sale-how-to-save-20-on-playstation-portal-helldivers-2-dualsense-controller-and-more/1100-6529304/" data-ref-id="1100-6529304">20% off official PS5 accessories</a> when spend at least $100 on two or more eligible items--including the PS Portal and DualSense Edge--at the PlayStation Direct online store.</p><div data-embed-type="pinbox" data-ref-id="4304">  <ul>                              <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/ps5-accessory-sale-how-to-save-20-on-playstation-portal-helldivers-2-dualsense-controller-and-more/1100-6529304/">PS5 Accessory Sale - How To Save 20% On PlayStation Portal, Helldivers 2 DualSense Controller, And More</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/like-a-dragon-pirate-yakuza-in-hawaii-preorder-deals-collectors-edition-amazon/1100-6526606/">Like A Dragon: Pirate Yakuza In Hawaii Collector's Edition In Stock At Amazon</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/save-on-sid-meiers-civilization-7-preorders-for-pc-mac-early-access-starts-february-6/1100-6525971/">Save On Sid Meier's Civilization 7 Preorders For PC &amp; Mac - Early Access Starts February 6</a></li>                          <li>         <span>+ Show More More Gaming, Tech, and Entertainment Deals &amp; Preorders Links (5)</span>       </li>          <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/apple-airpods-4-discounted-to-only-100-at-amazon/1100-6526375/">Apple AirPods 4 Discounted To Only $100 At Amazon</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/fortnite-festival-riffmaster-guitar-controller-gets-biggest-discount-yet/1100-6528970/">Fortnite Festival Riffmaster Guitar Controller Gets Biggest Discount Yet</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/monster-hunter-wilds-preorders-where-to-get-steelbook-edition-and-best-deals/1100-6526687/">Monster Hunter Wilds Preorders - Where To Get Steelbook Edition And Best Deals</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/geforce-rtx-50-series-gpus-launched-today-but-its-not-easy-to-grab-one/1100-6528684/">GeForce RTX 50-Series GPUs Launched Today, But It's Not Easy To Grab One</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/alienware-rtx-50-series-gaming-pcs-are-up-for-preorder-for-a-small-fortune/1100-6529159/">Alienware RTX 50-Series Gaming PCs Are Up For Preorder For A Small Fortune</a></li>   </ul> </div>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
